00:02:54.907 --> 00:02:58.435
the limit as n approaches
infinity of a sub-n,

00:02:58.435 --> 00:03:00.654
which is, I'll write in that red color,

00:03:00.654 --> 00:03:04.821
which is two to the nth power
over three to the n minus one

00:03:07.178 --> 00:03:11.345
over b sub-n, over two to the
