00:03:14.070 --> 00:03:15.855
So let me actually do a little

00:03:15.855 --> 00:03:17.539
algebraic manipulation right over here.

00:03:17.539 --> 00:03:19.735
This is going to to be the same thing as

00:03:19.735 --> 00:03:23.485
two to the nth over
three to the n minus one,

00:03:24.416 --> 00:03:27.499
times three to the n, over two the n.

00:03:29.910 --> 00:03:31.646
Divide the numerator and the denominators

00:03:31.646 --> 00:03:34.034
