00:03:34.034 --> 00:03:38.438
and so this will give
us, this will give us

00:03:38.438 --> 00:03:42.506
three to the n over
three to the n minus one.

00:03:42.506 --> 00:03:44.366
We can divide the numerator
and the denominator

00:03:44.366 --> 00:03:46.167
